    <title>LeetCode 2028. 找出缺失的观测数据</title>
    <link href="https://s1koy.github.io/2022/03/27/LeetCode-2028-%E6%89%BE%E5%87%BA%E7%BC%BA%E5%A4%B1%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%82%E6%B5%8B%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE/"/>
